<h1 class=3D"sub-title">
        The Best Classical Albums of 2025
    </h1>
<p>
<span class=3D"published-date">
                Tuesday, December 9, 2025
            </span>
</p>
<p class=3D"excerpt">
<strong>If you are searching for an inspirational new recording, look no furt=
her. All of these outstanding classical albums were Editor's Choices in Gramo=
phone magazine and are highly recommended</strong>
</p>
<div id=3D"rich-text">
<p class=3D"p1"><img alt=3D"" data-udi=3D"umb://media/b1083cb924794fc2b46ee5c=
e5f97f703" src=3D"https://www.gramophone.co.uk/media/259948/gramophone-best-o=
f-2025.jpg?width=3D800&amp;height=3D533.6" style=3D"width: 800px; height: 533=
.6px;"/></p>
<p class=3D"p1">In every issue of<span>=C2=A0</span><em>Gramophone</em>, Edit=
or Martin Cullingford chooses 10 new releases as his Editor's Choice selectio=
n. Below, you will find all of the albums selected as Editor's Choice in 2025=
, with the most recent releases at the top of the list.=C2=A0</p>
<p class=3D"p1">Members of the <em>Gramophone</em> Full Club and <em>Gramopho=
ne</em> Digital Club can access our Reviews Database, a digital archive of al=
l of our reviews from 1983 to today, with all of the new issue's reviews avai=
lable on the day of publication. To find out more about subscribing to<span>=
=C2=A0</span><em>Gramophone<span>=C2=A0</span></em>and the Reviews Database,=
=C2=A0please visit:<span>=C2=A0</span><a href=3D"https://www.magsubscriptions=
.com/music-gramophone" rel=3D"noopener" target=3D"_blank"><strong>magsubscrip=
tions.com</strong></a></p>
<h2><strong><img alt=3D"" data-udi=3D"umb://media/a216b52da69a49c39fd8368131d=
5f137" src=3D"https://www.gramophone.co.uk/media/259862/donizetti-lucia-di-la=
mmermoor-sols-orchestra-of-the-teatro-massimo-bellini-catania-fabrizio-maria-=
carminati-euroarts.jpg?width=3D800&amp;height=3D800" style=3D"width: 800px; h=
eight: 800px;"/></strong></h2>
<h2><strong>Donizetti </strong>Lucia di Lammermoor</h2>
<p><strong>Sols; Orchestra of the Teatro Massimo Bellini, Catania / Fabrizio =
Maria Carminati </strong>(EuroArts)</p>
<p>Soprano Lisette Oropesa excels in one of the pinnacles of the bel canto re=
pertoire, the lead in a superb line-up of singers, in a studio recording prod=
uced with panache.</p>
<p><a href=3D"https://www.gramophone.co.uk/review/donizetti-lucia-di-lammermo=
or-carminati"><strong>Read the <em>Gramophone</em> review</strong></a></p>
<hr/>
<h2><strong><img alt=3D"" data-udi=3D"umb://media/faef1803421643de950f8905e79=
e934d" src=3D"https://www.gramophone.co.uk/media/259861/ade-s-elgar-violin-co=
ncertos-christian-tetzlaff-vn-bbc-philharmonic-orchestra-_-john-storga-rds-on=
dine.png?width=3D800&amp;height=3D800" style=3D"width: 800px; height: 800px;"=
/></strong></h2>
